title: My 12 Books - November 2017 (gnv64)
description: A collection of 12 books for this month. 10 ePUBs and 2 PDFs, covers included in separate folder: 01. Hot Lights, Cold Steel by Michael J. Collins 02. Shadow of a Thief: A Thriller by Norman Gteen 07. Spellcasting for Beginners: A Simple Guide to Magical Practice by Michael Furie 08. Springer Handbook of Spacetime by Abhay Ashtekar and Vesselin Petkov 09. Stalin: Waiting for Hitler, 1929-1941 by Stephen Kotkin 10. That Last Weekend: A Novel of Suspense by Laura DiSilverio 11. The Energy Wise Home: Practical Ideas for Saving Energy, Money, and the Planet by Jeff Dondero 12. The O.
